Air Canada, Union Fail to Reach Agreement After Negotiations Last Night

-- B y   T i m   S m i t h
-- 
2011-09-20T04:22:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/cupe-union-says-no-deal-with-air-canada-after-negotiations.html
Canada’s CUPE union said it hasn’t
reached a deal with  Air Canada (AC/A)  after talks ended on Monday night
and hopes to resume discussions on Tuesday, according to a
statement on the MWR wire today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
